:: 1. Clean up "ghost" lines (lines that contain only spaces/tabs but look empty)
"^[ \t]+$"->"EMPTY"x

:: 2. Convert bullets, preserving indentation (Matches any indent + bullet + space)
"^([ \t]*)â€¢\s+"->"$1- "

:: 3. Bold the Key terms (Matches indent + dash + text + colon)
"^(\s*-\s*)([^:\n]+):"->"$1**$2:**"

:: 4. Normalize newlines: Reduce 3 or more newlines to just 2 (Prevents huge gaps)
"\n{3,}"->"\n\n"

:: 5. Tighten Lists: If there is a blank line before a bullet, remove it (Makes lists compact)
"\n\n(\s*- )"->"\n$1"

:: 6. Ensure Headers have space above them (Adds breathing room before ## Headers)
"\n+(?=##)"->"\n\n"